reviewText:
Pros:

- One of the funniest games I've ever played;
- Creative gameplay;
- Good storyline;
- A great number of combinations, upgrades and goals to reach;

Cons:

- There's a few extensive levels;
- Some of the soundtracks may be repetitive.

Rating: 100/100 A MUST HAVE!

